com.jaspersoft.jasperserver.jrsh.operation.grammar.token

Interface Token

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractToken, AnyStringToken, FileNameToken, RepositoryToken, StringToken

    public interface Token
    A token is a structure representing a lexeme that explicitly indicates its categorization for the purpose of parsing. For more info please visit wiki page https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lexical_analysis#Token

    2.0
    Author:
